<p>The loss of a friend is a deeply personal experience. These messages aim to provide comfort and support to your friend during this difficult time. Keep it simple, personal and let them know you're there for them.</p>
<li>I'm so incredibly sorry to hear about your loss. My thoughts are with you.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and sending love during this heartbreaking time.</li>
<li> Your friend was such a special person, and I will miss them dearly.</li>
<li> I'll always remember your friend's (positive quality).  They'll be greatly missed.</li>
<li> Please accept my deepest condolences.</li>
<li> Know that I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li> I am here for you if you need to talk, cry, or just be quiet.</li>
<li> Sending strength and comfort your way.</li>
<li> I'm so sorry for your loss. May you find peace.</li>
<li> My heart goes out to you during this painful time.</li>
